title: Zombie Diets
description:
Written by Kristy Lopez-Bernal
Starring: Jonathan Marballi, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Langan Kingsley, Zack Phillips, Alene Latimer, Kerry O'Brien, Jon Bershad, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Kelly Hudson.

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, October 21, 2013.

Filmed by Jocelyne Jo Roueiheb and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
